+     ORACLE DATABASE 19C DATAGUARD PHYSICAL STANDBY      +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

#NOTE
Make sure primary is in archivelog mode;
Check FORCE LOGGING is enabled;

#ON PRIMARY
sqlplus / as sysdba

SQL*Plus: Release 19.0.0.0.0 - Production on Sat Mar 14 15:36:05 2020
Version 19.3.0.0.0
